# 摘要

CLion 输出遇到中文乱码解决办法



CLion 输出遇到乱码解决办法

```c++
#include <iostream>
int main()
{
    std::string str = "我叫张三,我喜欢编程";
    std::cout << "str: " << str << std::endl;
    return 0;
}
```

//输出
str: 鎴戝彨寮犱笁,鎴戝枩娆㈢紪绋

//更改设置
File -> Settings -> Default Settings -> Editor -> File Encodings:
Global Encoding: UTF-8
Project Encoding : UTF-8
Default encoding for properties files: UTF-8
